episodes.title: How Two Men Escaped Jonestown 😱 What They Saw Inside the Cult 😨 (HD)
episodes.description:
🏃‍♂️😱 Two men ran from hell. This documentary reveals how Stanley Clayton and Tim Carter escaped the Jonestown massacre and lived to tell the story.

📼✨ Their real-time recollections uncover one of the most terrifying survival stories ever recorded.

🎬 What You’ll See:
— 🎤 First-hand survivor testimony.
— 🏃‍♂️ How they escaped the compound.
— 🎞️ Rare footage from Guyana.
— 🧠 Psychological survival.
— 🕯️ The truth behind the final hours.

📺 About the Documentary:
This film tells the story of the only two men who escaped Jim Jones’ mass suicide — revealing what happened inside Jonestown before the poison was drunk.
